{"_path":"/maps/_photography","_dir":"maps","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"摄影","description":"技术传达情感，摄影记录生活。","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"怎么衡量一张照片的好坏"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"怎么衡量一张照片的好坏？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"摄影是摄影师想法及内容的表达，所以照片好坏关乎其主题是否明确，内容是否有趣，及想法的传达是否到位。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"技术是围绕想法服务的，所以摄影需要有摄影师的思考构思，而不单纯是一种记录。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"光圈和景深的关系"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"光圈和景深的关系？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"光圈大，景深小，虚化强"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"光圈快门iso-cheat-sheet"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"光圈、快门、ISO Cheat Sheet"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"光圈","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202411090118055.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"快门","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202411090127871.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"ISO","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/202411090128878.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"不同自动快门模式适合什么场景"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不同自动快门模式适合什么场景？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"一般有 M 档，Av 档，Tv 档。Av 档光圈优先适合人像、风景、微距等固定光圈以达特定虚化效果的场景。Tv 档快门优先适合运动、动态场景，如体育摄影、街拍等。M 档手动模式适合特殊场景，如夜景、星空、棚内摄影等。"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_photography:0.index.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_photography/0.index.md","_stem":"6.maps/_photography/0.index",